---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-20 border-t-2 border-primary/20 bg-card/50 backdrop-blur-sm">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="text-center space-y-4">
      <div class="inline-block bg-accent text-accent-foreground px-6 py-3 -rotate-1 shadow-md border-2 border-primary/30 transition-transform hover:rotate-1 hover:scale-102">
        <p class="font-medium">© {currentYear} 比特毯子 - 记录学习，分享成长</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
        软件分享 • AI编程 • 学习记录
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors">
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a href="https://bilibili.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors">
          Bilibili
        </a>
        <a href="/rss.xml" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors">
          RSS
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
